{"tid":1505384,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"既然大部分人都無膽硬碰硬 就請發夢入機場","createTime":"2019-08-25T13:57:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T01:30:01.000Z","uid":108305,"like":42,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"3903b4e2c59e7c3e7e3a20436e8b02cbe40b19d5","tid":1505384,"uid":108305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:57:03.000Z","msg":"首先 核彈都唔割<br />\n但實在發夢見到太多人今日係前線既表現係強差人意<br />\n企前 整路障 守 差佬到 走唔切 被人拉<br />\n唔夠膽還手 連去救返手足都唔敢 睇到眼都突埋<br />\n警犬連支炮都攞埋射埋 老黑call大隊尋仇<br />\n都係乜都做唔到<br />\n我已經係兩個月前講過香港人既包袱問題<br />\n咁樣做長遠係完全冇意思<br />\n<br />\n既然如此 點解唔放棄十八區遊行？<br />\n之後周末轉場去機場<br />\n呢個已經有好多人講係最大春袋<br />\n代價低 成效反響大 性價比咁高 又唔洗怕有包袱<br />\n要記住 咁樣既硬碰硬對政府既影響極少 唔會因為咁讓步<br />\n只有經濟 國際壓力 先至係政府跪低既主因<br />\n請大家黎緊發夢去機場 只有咁先係出路"},{"pid":"19270056f5263f7596818f977f013d8c7970201b","tid":1505384,"uid":167467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:58:51.000Z","msg":"有冇可能再次發動一人一post"},{"pid":"067664a5ce1a7cafd77102c0d8c1401ec4486ac9","tid":1505384,"uid":259613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:00:29.000Z","msg":"入機場入機場入機場入機場入機場入機場入機場"},{"pid":"a66312e0f0fddcd5ad1c35bcb59811e461d3ecb0","tid":1505384,"uid":108305,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:00:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cJFrmBy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcJFrmBy.jpg&h=3ca23e7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8ePfZoe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8ePfZoe.jpg&h=ef10774b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ur03oPU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUr03oPU.jpg&h=c66720d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G51aOgA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG51aOgA.jpg&h=c7cef675&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55ae93cc6d123ff5ac566cb60d9e42ac234200a8","tid":1505384,"u